GCODING.item: APPEND LINES OF it_disp to it_loc .
*LOOP AT it_val INTO wa_val WHERE palid = wa_disp-palid .
*delete it_val WHERE palid = wa_val-palid and matnr = wa_val-matnr .
READ TABLE it_disp INTO wa_loc index 1.
* DELETE it_pallet WHERE cdate ne s_date .
* READ TABLE it_makt into wa_makt with key matnr = wa_pallet-matnr .
* concatenate gv_day gv_date gv_year into gv_date separated by '.'.
* concatenate gv_hr gv_mnt gv_sec into gv_hr separated by ':'.
